<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>Broken Access Control 방어 버전</title>
  <link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">

  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-16 p-8 bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">Broken Access Control 방어 버전</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
      URL 파라미터는 화이트리스트에 등록된 파일명만 허용합니다.
    </p>

    <form action="/lesson/bac_secure/file" method="get" class="space-y-4">
      <label class="block text-gray-700">
        파일명:
        <input
          type="text"
          name="file"
          value="<%= file %>"
          placeholder="public.txt"
          required
          class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring"
        />
      </label>
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-green-700 transition"
      >
        안전 파일 조회
      </button>
    </form>

    <p class="mt-4 text-center">
      <a href="/lesson/bac" class="underline text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800">
        ← 취약 버전으로 돌아가기
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>